  <sect3 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to Five or More</title>

    <para>
      <application>five-or-more</application> is a
      puzzle game, where the objective is to align as 
      often as possible five or more objects of the same color 
      and shape causing them to disappear.
    </para>

    &lfs76_checked;

